{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Apply all employment rights from the start of employment ",
        "additional_details": "I would like the government to help people have a more stable and secure life in employment giving people stronger employment rights from the beginning of their employment.  \r\n \r\nThis would mean that people that are treated unfairly can bring a claim to tribunal for unfair dismissal before the 2 year employment rules kick in. This could help reduce unemployment for those treated unfairly during their employment.\r\n",
        "background": "Currently certain employment rights including the right to claim unfair dismissal and the right to statutory redundancy pay only apply after a minimum of 2 year\u2019s continuous service. ",
